               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla samāʿtāta Ṗarāqliṭos “Vita of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos” (fols.
                     3ra-15vb) 
 - Introduction (fols. 3ra-3vb) 
 II) Taʾammǝra samāʿtāta
                     Ṗarāqliṭos “Miracles of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos”: 12 miracles (fols.
                     15vb-30vb) 
 - Introduction (fols. 15vb-17rb)
 
                     Colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5877DossierParaqlitos">Hagiographic Dossier of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos</title>
                     <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3ra" to="15vb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1491Gadlas">Gadla Ṣādǝqān za-Ṗarāqliṭos</title>
                        <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.1">
                           <locus from="3ra" to="3vb"/>
                           <title>Introduction</title>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="15vb" to="30vb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5878MiraclesParaqlitos"> Taʾammǝra samāʿtāta Ṗarāqliṭos: 12 miracles</title>
                        <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="15vb" to="17rb"/>
                           <title>Introduction</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <note>In this Ms., miracle 3 (corresponding to <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap046#p2_i2.4"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: ESap046#p2_i2.4</span></ref>) 
                           has been divided into two independent miracles: miracle 3 corresponding to 
                           <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap046#p2_i2.4"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: ESap046#p2_i2.4</span><locus from="53ra" to="56ra"/></ref> 
                           and miracle 4 corresponding to 
                           <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap046#p2_i2.4"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: ESap046#p2_i2.4</span><locus from="56ra" to="59ra"/></ref>
                           . As a consequence, the
                           total number of the miracles is 12; they are not numbered.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#30vb">30vb</locus>
                        ተፈጸመት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አመ፴ሁ፡ ለጥር፡ በ፲፱፸፱ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡
                        በዘመነ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ዘወሀባ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ጰራቅሊጦስ፡ አቶ፡ ጰራቅሊጦ[ስ]፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ [vac] ከመ፡ ይኩኖሙ፡
                        መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ <note>The note states that the Ms. was completed on the 30th of
                        Ṭǝrr in the year of mercy 1979, during the time of the Evangelist Luke (= <date when="1987">25
                        January 1987 A.D.</date>). Besides, it is said that ʾato Ṗarāqliṭos Ḫāyla Śǝllāse
                           (?) donated it to the tābot of the church, together with his wife, whose name
                        however is missing. </note></colophon>
                     
                     
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
