                              <abbr>የ፡ ም፡</abbr> for <expan>የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#15vb">15vb</locus>, 21rb, 22va).</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Holy names; the names of the Trinity; the name
                           Ṗarāqliṭos and the name of other protagonists; the name of the
                           donors.
 A few lines alternating with black lines in the incipit page
                           of Text I; incipit of Text II and of each miracle; the initial words of
                           some paragraphs in Texts I and II; some interlineal corrections (e.g.,
                           fol. 12rb).
 Elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic
                           numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
